### Multi-Tenant SaaS API - Memberships
### VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client compatible

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get tokens first by running auth.http login
@accessToken = {{$dotenv %ACCESS_TOKEN}}
@tenantId = {{$dotenv %TENANT_ID}}
@membershipId = replace-with-membership-id

### Invite a user to the tenant
# @name invite
POST {{baseUrl}}/memberships/invite
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

{
  "email": "newmember@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

### Update member role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/memberships/{{membershipId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

{
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Remove a member
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/memberships/{{membershipId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Leave the tenant (as current user)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/memberships/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
